I guess on this whole record I
was thinking about how much

00:19:28.730 --> 00:19:35.000
noise there is and what of it
is actually important, and

00:19:35.000 --> 00:19:37.576
what of it is actually
just noise.

00:19:37.576 --> 00:19:45.150
And somehow I got to thinking
about how Jesus and Robert

00:19:45.150 --> 00:19:48.910
Johnson probably were in the
exact same position when they

00:19:48.910 --> 00:19:52.430
were about to make these big
decisions in their life like,

00:19:52.430 --> 00:19:55.030
I need to get born, or, I need
to sell my soul to the devil

00:19:55.030 --> 00:19:56.620
so I can play guitar.

00:19:56.620 --> 00:20:00.510
